          <name>NETMIDI2_SESSION_IDLE</name>
          <briefdescription>
<para>Device may be aware of each other (e.g. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>through mDNS), however neither device has sent an Invitation. The two Devices are not in a Session. </para>
          </detaileddescription>
        </enumvalue>
