          <name>NETMIDI2_SESSION_PENDING_RESET</name>
          <briefdescription>
<para>One Device has sent the Session Reset Command and is waiting for Session Reset Reply, and a timeout has not yet occurred. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
